message.content: cs.LO, cs.SY, cs.RO, cs.PL, cs.ET - The paper proposes a framework for the synthesis of controllers using energy timed automata, which involves logical and optimization aspects. Therefore, it is likely to belong to the Logic in Computer Science (cs.LO), Systems and Control (cs.SY), Robotics (cs.RO), Programming Languages (cs.PL), and Emerging Technologies (cs.ET) sub-categories.
